<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://demos.creative-tim.com/marketplace/soft-ui-design-system-pro/assets/css/soft-design-system-pro.min.css?v=1.1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:700,900">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>
<body>
    
    <h1>Pesquisa de Satisfação</h1>
    <h2>Gostaríamos de receber sua avaliação sobre os serviços prestados pela ConLine e <br> agradecemos desde já pelos números informados!</h2>

    <section id="formulario">
		<div class="container py-4">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-8 mx-auto d-flex justify-content-center flex-column">
					<form role="form" id="contact-form" method="post" autocomplete="off">
						<div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-12"> <!--  PRIMEIRA PERGUNTA  -->
                                    <label class="pergunta">Qual nota você daria para o nosso atendimento comercial?</label>
                                    <div class="notas p1">
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ff9eae" value="0" >0</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffafbc" value="1" >1</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffafbc" value="2" >2</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffc0cb" value="3" >3</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffd1d9" value="4" >4</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffe2e7" value="5" >5</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #fff3f5" value="6" >6</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="passive p" style="background-color: #efffef" value="7" >7</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="passive p" style="background-color: #dcffdc" value="8" >8</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="promoter p" style="background-color: #adecba" value="9" >9</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="promoter p" style="background-color: #5ad974" value="10" >10</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-12"> <!--  SEGUNDA PERGUNTA  -->
                                    <label class="pergunta">Qual nota você daria para o nosso atendimento operacional?</label>
                                    <div class="notas p2">
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ff9eae" value="0" >0</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffafbc" value="1" >1</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffafbc" value="2" >2</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffc0cb" value="3" >3</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffd1d9" value="4" >4</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffe2e7" value="5" >5</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #fff3f5" value="6" >6</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="passive p" style="background-color: #efffef" value="7" >7</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="passive p" style="background-color: #dcffdc" value="8" >8</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="promoter p" style="background-color: #adecba" value="9" >9</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="promoter p" style="background-color: #5ad974" value="10" >10</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-12"> <!--  TERCEIRA PERGUNTA  -->
                                    <label class="pergunta">Qual nota você daria para o nosso atendimento financeiro?</label>
                                    <div class="notas p3">
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ff9eae" value="0" >0</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffafbc" value="1" >1</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffafbc" value="2" >2</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffc0cb" value="3" >3</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffd1d9" value="4" >4</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #ffe2e7" value="5" >5</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="detractor p" style="background-color: #fff3f5" value="6" >6</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="passive p" style="background-color: #efffef" value="7" >7</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="passive p" style="background-color: #dcffdc" value="8" >8</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="promoter p" style="background-color: #adecba" value="9" >9</button>
                                        <button type="button" class="promoter p" style="background-color: #5ad974" value="10" >10</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="container py-4">
                                <div class="form-wrapper">
                                    <label class="pergunta">De forma geral, você está satisfeito com o nosso serviço?</label>
                                    <p class="text-center"></p>
                                    <div class="smiles d-flex justify-content-around">
                                        <div class="smile" id="satisfeito" onclick="ativarSmile(this)">
                                            <svg style="width:24px;height:24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path fill="#000000" d="M20,12A8,8 0 0,0 12,4A8,8 0 0,0 4,12A8,8 0 0,0 12,20A8,8 0 0,0 20,12M22,12A10,10 0 0,1 12,22A10,10 0 0,1 2,12A10,10 0 0,1 12,2A10,10 0 0,1 22,12M10,9.5C10,10.3 9.3,11 8.5,11C7.7,11 7,10.3 7,9.5C7,8.7 7.7,8 8.5,8C9.3,8 10,8.7 10,9.5M17,9.5C17,10.3 16.3,11 15.5,11C14.7,11 14,10.3 14,9.5C14,8.7 14.7,8 15.5,8C16.3,8 17,8.7 17,9.5M12,17.23C10.25,17.23 8.71,16.5 7.81,15.42L9.23,14C9.68,14.72 10.75,15.23 12,15.23C13.25,15.23 14.32,14.72 14.77,14L16.19,15.42C15.29,16.5 13.75,17.23 12,17.23Z" />
                                            </svg>
                                            <div class="text">Sim</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="smile" id="insatisfeito" onclick="ativarSmile(this)">
                                            <svg style="width:24px;height:24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path fill="#000000" d="M20,12A8,8 0 0,0 12,4A8,8 0 0,0 4,12A8,8 0 0,0 12,20A8,8 0 0,0 20,12M22,12A10,10 0 0,1 12,22A10,10 0 0,1 2,12A10,10 0 0,1 12,2A10,10 0 0,1 22,12M15.5,8C16.3,8 17,8.7 17,9.5C17,10.3 16.3,11 15.5,11C14.7,11 14,10.3 14,9.5C14,8.7 14.7,8 15.5,8M10,9.5C10,10.3 9.3,11 8.5,11C7.7,11 7,10.3 7,9.5C7,8.7 7.7,8 8.5,8C9.3,8 10,8.7 10,9.5M12,14C13.75,14 15.29,14.72 16.19,15.81L14.77,17.23C14.32,16.5 13.25,16 12,16C10.75,16 9.68,16.5 9.23,17.23L7.81,15.81C8.71,14.72 10.25,14 12,14Z" />
                                            </svg>
                                            <div class="text">Não</div>
                                        </div>
                            
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-group">
                                        <label for="details">Feedbacks e Sugestões</label>
                                        <textarea class="form-control" id="details" rows="2"></textarea>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="btn btn-secondary btn-block col-md-12" id="yes" onclick="confirmar()">Confirmar!</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
					</form>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

    <script src="./script.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
</body>
</html>